    Page: 430
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Heterodoxy And Deviation=‘And Ye Shall Be as Gods’
By: Sri Sankarâchârya
---
To know the real Self to be one’s own is the greatest attainment
according to the scriptures and reasoning. To know wrongly the
non-Self such as the ego etc. to be the Self is no attainment at all.
One, therefore, should renounce this misconception of taking the
non-Self for the Self.
